{"id":"mai-z3l2","kind":"decision","title":"Default docs dir is .mai-docs, not docs/","edges":[{"type":"targets","target":{"kind":"path","ref":"docs/DESIGN.md"}}],"body":"Maitake working docs (specs, ADRs, research, plans) are for the team and agents, not end users. Defaulting to docs/ collides with user-facing documentation (mdbook, docusaurus, README).\n\nDefault: .mai-docs/ (gitignored by mai init)\nPower users: docs.dir = \"docs\" in global config\n\nThis eliminates the git-tracked heuristic entirely — everything in the mai docs dir is maitake's territory. No isGitTracked check needed. Auto-import all files without mai-id frontmatter.\n\nRationale: AI/LLM spec docs don't need to be the user-facing docs/ folder.","timestamp":"2026-03-29T05:55:45Z","branch":"main"}
